original_title: Diana Ross & the Supremes - Live  at the Rai Congress Center in Amsterdam
overview: The Supremes perform live in Amsterdam on January 16, 1968. They play a number of medleys, originals, and covers. This would see a 2006 DVD release retitled as "The Supremes Greatest Hits - Live in Amsterdam."
title: Diana Ross & the Supremes - Live  at the Rai Congress Center in Amsterdam
